<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><author>Pliney Fisk, Tune: &quot;Watchman tell us&quot;</author>
<hymn_number>121</hymn_number>
<title>Watchman Tell Us ƲIT121</title>
<aka>Chihowa Ushi mak hosh</aka>
<lyrics>[V1]
 Chihowa Ushi mak hosh
 Ʋba ya̱ mihintishke;
 Nan isht a holitopa
 Moma ilai eshi hosh
 Ʋba ya̱ mihintishke;
 Nan u̱ha im ʋlhtaha
 Holitopa ai a̱hlit
 Ʋba ya̱ mihintishke.

[V2]
 Chisʋs afama chi̱ kʋt
 Hʋchim ʋlhtaha hoh cho?
 Chihowa Ushi mak osh
 Ʋba ya̱ mihintishke;
 Chihowa Ushi mak osh
 Okla mom' i̱ haiakʋt,
 Ʋba minti ka pisá;
 Hʋsh afama chi̱ hoke.</lyrics>
</song>